<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <title>SecureBuddy</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css" />

    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="main">
      <h1 class="heading">Welcome to SecureBuddy</h1>
      <form action="/" method="post">
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="repository-link" class="form-label">Repository Link *</label>
          <input type="url" name="repoUrl" class="form-control" id="repository-link" placeholder="" required/>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
      </form>
      <div class="resultBox">
        <hr>
        <h1>Result</h1>
        <h5>Scanned Repo: <%= repoUrl %></h5>
        <p>
          <i>Repository Score :</i>
          <span id="vulnerability_score"> <%= repoScore %></span>
        </p>
        <p>
          <i>Trust Score :</i> <span id="trust_score"><%= trustScore %></span>
        </p>
        <% if (repoScore >= 70){ %>
        <p>
          <i>Conclusion about repository:</i>
          <span>This repo does not contain any high-level or critical-level
            vulnerabilities. That means the repository is safe.</span>
        </p>

        <% }else if(repoScore > 30){ %>
        <p>
          <i>Conclusion about repository:</i>
          <span>There might be high-level and critical-level vulnerabilities
            present in the repo. This repository may or may not be safe.</span
          >
        </p>

        <% }else{ %>
        <p>
          <i>Conclusion about repository:</i>
          <span
            >This repo contains a large number of critical-level and high-level
            vulnerabilities. That means the repository is not safe.
          </span>
        </p>

        <% } %> <% if (trustScore > 70){ %>
        <p>
          <i>Conclusion about author:</i>
          <span>The author of this repo is trustworthy and genuine. You can trust the author.</span>
        </p>

        <% }else if(trustScore > 30){ %>
        <p>
          <i>Conclusion about author:</i>
          <span>The author of this repo may or may not be trustworthy.</span>
        </p>

        <% }else{ %>
        <p>
          <i>Conclusion about author: </i>
          <span>
            The author of this repo is not trustworthy and genuine. You can't trust the author.</span>
        </p>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <footer>Note: SecureBuddy supports only Github repositories and Java, JavaScript, Python, PHP, Ruby, Scala, .NET, Golang, and C/C++ languages.</footer>
    </div>
  </body>
  
</html>
